snippet.title: Asphalt Legends Unite - Showcase
snippet.description:
Tune in to the Asphalt Legends Unite Showcase!
Join the team as they take the stage to preview everything you can expect on the release of Asphalt Legends Unite, this July 17th!

Play Asphalt: http://gmlft.co/A9YTDL

To get the latest news from Asphalt, follow us on:
Facebook Asphalt Legends Unite: https://www.facebook.com/PlayAsphaltUnite
Twitter: https://twitter.com/asphalt
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/asphaltgames
Discord: https://discord.gg/asphaltlegendsunite
